data.description: This beautiful 4BR/3BA Killearn home has all the charm and warmth of a mountain house, right here in Tallahassee! Enjoy the wood burning fireplace, overlooking a woodsy ravine with a gentle stream below. Listen to the birds while having your morning coffee, on the huge screened back porch. Cook out and watch the game from the back deck. There is plenty of space for hobbies or an in-law suite or home office in the walk-out basement. What are you waiting for?! Come make this your home for the holidays now! Home sold as is with right to inspect, all measurements approximate and buyer should verify. Sq ft includes heated and cooled finished basement.
